    image: url(data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMjAiIGhlaWdodD0iMjAiIHZpZXdCb3g9IjAgMCAyMCAyMCIgZmlsbD0ibm9uZSIgeG1sbnM9Imh0dHA6Ly93d3cudzMub3JnLzIwMDAvc3ZnIj4KPHBhdGggZD0iTTUgOEwxMCAxM0wxNSA4IiBzdHJva2U9IiMwMDAwMDAiIHN0cm9rZS13aWR0aD0iMyIgc3Ryb2tlLWxpbmVjYXA9InJvdW5kIiBzdHJva2UtbGluZWpvaW49InJvdW5kIi8+Cjwvc3ZnPgo=);
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
}

QComboBox QAbstractItemView {
    background-color: @surface;
    color: @on-surface;
    border: 1.5px solid @border;
    border-radius: 0;
    selection-background-color: @selected;
    selection-color: @on-primary;
    outline: none;
}

QComboBox QAbstractItemView::item {
    padding: 12px;
    min-height: 24px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid @border;
    font-weight: 600;
}

QComboBox QAbstractItemView::item:hover {
    background-color: @hover;
    border: 1.5px solid @border;
}

/* ===== SPIN BOX ===== */

QSpinBox, QDoubleSpinBox {
    background-color: @surface;
    color: @on-surface;
    border: 1.5px solid @border;
    border-radius: 0;
    padding: 8px;
    selection-background-color: @selected;
    selection-color: @on-primary;
    font-weight: 600;
}

QSpinBox:focus, QDoubleSpinBox:focus {
    border: 1.5px solid @accent;
}

QSpinBox::up-button, QDoubleSpinBox::up-button {
    background-color: @surface;
    border: 1px solid @border;
    width: 20px;
    padding-right: 4px;
}

QSpinBox::down-button, QDoubleSpinBox::down-button {
    background-color: @surface;
    border: 1px solid @border;
    width: 20px;
    padding-right: 4px;
}

/* ===== CHECK BOX ===== */

QCheckBox {
    color: @on-surface;
    spacing: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
}

QCheckBox::indicator {
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    border: 1.5px solid @border;
    border-radius: 0;
    background-color: @surface;
}

QCheckBox::indicator:hover {
    border: 1.5px solid @accent;
}

QCheckBox::indicator:checked {
    background-color: @accent;
    border: 1.5px solid @border;
    image: url(data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMTYiIGhlaWdodD0iMTYiIHZpZXdCb3g9IjAgMCAxNiAxNiIgZmlsbD0ibm9uZSIgeG1sbnM9Imh0dHA6Ly93d3cudzMub3JnLzIwMDAvc3ZnIj4KPHBhdGggZD0iTTEzIDVMNiAxMkwzIDkiIHN0cm9rZT0iI0ZGRkZGRiIgc3Ryb2tlLXdpZHRoPSIzIiBzdHJva2UtbGluZWNhcD0icm91bmQiIHN0cm9rZS1saW5lam9pbj0icm91bmQiLz4KPC9zdmc+);
}

QCheckBox::indicator:disabled {
    border: 1.5px solid @disabled;
    background-color: @hover;
}

/* ===== RADIO BUTTON ===== */

QRadioButton {
    color: @on-surface;
    spacing: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
}

QRadioButton::indicator {
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    border: 1.5px solid @border;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background-color: @surface;
}

QRadioButton::indicator:hover {
    border: 1.5px solid @accent;
}

QRadioButton::indicator:checked {
    background-color: @accent;
    border: 1.5px solid @border;
    image: url(data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMTAiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAiIHZpZXdCb3g9IjAgMCAxMCAxMCIgZmlsbD0ibm9uZSIgeG1sbnM9Imh0dHA6Ly93d3cudzMub3JnLzIwMDAvc3ZnIj4KPGNpcmNsZSBjeD0iNSIgY3k9IjUiIHI9IjUiIGZpbGw9IiNGRkZGRkYiLz4KPC9zdmc+);
}

QRadioButton::indicator:disabled {
    border: 1.5px solid @disabled;
    background-color: @hover;
}

/* ===== SLIDERS ===== */

QSlider::groove:horizontal {
    background-color: @border;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 0;
    border: 1px solid @border;
}

QSlider::handle:horizontal {
    background-color: @accent;
    border: 1.5px solid @border;
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    border-radius: 0;
    margin-top: -10px;
    margin-bottom: -10px;
}

QSlider::handle:horizontal:hover {
    background-color: @primary-variant;
    border: 1.5px solid @border;
}

QSlider::handle:horizontal:pressed {
    background-color: @pressed;
    border: 1.5px solid @border;
}

QSlider::sub-page:horizontal {
    background-color: @accent;
    border: 1px solid @border;
    border-radius: 0;
}

/* ===== PROGRESS BAR ===== */

QProgressBar {
    background-color: @surface;
    color: @on-surface;
    border: 1.5px solid @border;
    border-radius: 0;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2px;
    font-weight: 700;
}

QProgressBar::chunk {
    background-color: @accent;
    border: 1px solid @border;
    border-radius: 0;
}

/* ===== GROUP BOX ===== */

QGroupBox {
    color: @on-surface;
    border: 1.5px solid @border;
    border-radius: 0;
    margin: 16px 0px 0px 0px;
    padding-top: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
}

QGroupBox::title {
    color: @on-surface;
    subcontrol-origin: margin;
    left: 16px;
    padding: 0 12px 0 12px;
    background-color: @background;
    font-weight: 700;
}

/* ===== TAB WIDGET ===== */

QTabWidget::pane {
    background-color: @surface;
    border: 1.5px solid @border;
    border-radius: 0;
    margin-top: -2px;
}

QTabBar::tab {
    background-color: @background;
    color: @on-background;
    border: 1.5px solid @border;
    padding: 12px 20px;
    margin-right: 4px;
    border-top-left-radius: 0;
    border-top-right-radius: 0;
    border-bottom: none;
    font-weight: 700;
}

QTabBar::tab:selected {
    background-color: @surface;
    color: @on-surface;
    border-bottom: 1.5px solid @surface;
    border: 1.5px solid @border;
    border-bottom: none;
}

QTabBar::tab:hover:!selected {
    background-color: @hover;
    border: 1.5px solid @border;
    border-bottom: none;
}

/* ===== LIST WIDGET ===== */

QListWidget {
    background-color: @surface;
    color: @on-surface;
    border: 1.5px solid @border;
    border-radius: 0;
    padding: 8px;
    outline: none;
    selection-background-color: @selected;
    selection-color: @on-primary;
}

QListWidget::item {
    padding: 12px;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    border-radius: 0;
    margin: 2px;
    font-weight: 600;
}

QListWidget::item:selected {
    background-color: @selected;
    color: @on-primary;
    border: 1.5px solid @border;
}

QListWidget::item:hover:!selected {
    background-color: @hover;
    border: 1px solid @border;
}

/* ===== TREE WIDGET ===== */

QTreeWidget {
    background-color: @surface;
    color: @on-surface;
    border: 1.5px solid @border;
    border-radius: 0;
    outline: none;
    selection-background-color: @selected;
    selection-color: @on-primary;
}

QTreeWidget::item {
    padding: 8px;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    border-radius: 0;
    margin: 1px;
    font-weight: 600;
}

QTreeWidget::item:selected {
    background-color: @selected;
    color: @on-primary;
    border: 1.5px solid @border;
}

QTreeWidget::item:hover:!selected {
    background-color: @hover;
    border: 1px solid @border;
}

QTreeWidget::branch:closed:has-children {
    image: url(data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMTYiIGhlaWdodD0iMTYiIHZpZXdCb3g9IjAgMCAxNiAxNiIgZmlsbD0ibm9uZSIgeG1sbnM9Imh0dHA6Ly93d3cudzMub3JnLzIwMDAvc3ZnIj4KPHBhdGggZD0iTTYgNEwxMCA4TDYgMTJWNFoiIGZpbGw9IiMwMDAwMDAiLz4KPC9zdmc+);
}

